BukkitCommons 1.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons
Main package used for code compat with Bukkit API or smaller utilities that don't go with other packages
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.collect
Collections and custom implementation frameworks using the JCF
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.concurrent
Concurrency utils to assist with concurrent programming and multi-threaded safety
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.event
Event framework used to listen and call for events that are not suited for use by using the BukkitAPI PluginManager.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.instrument
Provides utilities for adding, removing, and modifying members such as fields, methods, and constructors, and even classes themselves.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.instrument.experimental
Experimental assembly modifications library, not production ready.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.instrument.refs
References to bytecode representations of structures such as the constant pool and its entries
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.io
IO utilities...
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.misc
Miscellaneous utilities, like ASCII table formatters and precodition checkers
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.nmsobc
Access to minecraft server internals
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.nmsobc.protocol
Access to the protocol of minecraft server, the communications between minecraft client and minecraft server.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.providers
Just lots of code used for other utilities in within the utils
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.reflection
Interfaces for weak access to implementations package used for fast reflection.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.reflection.chain
Reflection chaining is multiple reflective operations dependant on the result of the last in order to get the final result.
com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.reflection.impl
Implementations of Managers in com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.reflection package for faster reflection than legacy Java Reflection API.
